<br>
<!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><i> Verant says</i><!--EZCODE ITALIC END-->, &quot;Visit our message boards and tell us what you'd like to see in the game.&quot;<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> Verant means</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END-->, &quot;Visit our message boards and tell us what you'd like to see in the game that we feel like giving you.&quot;<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><i> Verant says</i><!--EZCODE ITALIC END-->, &quot;Visit our message boards and tell us about in-game bugs and issues so we can fix them.&quot;<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> Verant means</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END-->, &quot;Visit our message boards and tell us about those in-game bugs and issues we're willing to acknowledge... oh, and please forget about bothering us with issues that aren't biting us on the ass every time we turn around, because frankly, we don't think they exist until they do so.&quot;<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><i> Verant says</i><!--EZCODE ITALIC END-->, &quot;Come play an interactive roleplaying game where adventure and interactive events happen to increase your gaming pleasure!&quot;<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> Verant means</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END-->, &quot;Come play an interactive roleplaying game where you get whatever level of service we feel like giving you because we can't get the budget to actually PAY people to be there to service you. Oh, and by the way, if you want to pay another $30 a month, we'll actually go through the hassle of staffing up enough people to support ONE server where you get responsive service and interactive events... but don't expect us to give that to everyone... after all, we never intended you to think you would get the game AND service all at once.&quot;<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><i> Verant says</i><!--EZCODE ITALIC END-->, &quot;Visit our message boards and tell us how we can improve our service to you.&quot;<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> Verant means</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END-->, &quot;Lord, you really FELL for that one?&quot;<br>
